snippet.title: Tezotopia - The Future of Play-To-Earn NFT Gaming
snippet.description: Create, build, battle, and earn. Tezotopia is a futuristic space adventure built on the Tezos (XTZ) blockchain, that allows players to earn income from yield farming NFTs and waging battle against other players.
